{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-415-titanic-sets","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Učionica 415: Kolekcija Titaničkog","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Skup tačaka u ravni $S$ naziva se titanički skup ako postoji prava koja prolazi samo kroz dve tačke u $S$.</p>\n<p>Primer skupa Titanik je $S = \\{(0, 0), (0, 1), (0, 2), (1, 1), (2, 0), (1, 0)\\}$, gde linija koja prolazi kroz (0, 1) i (2, 0) ne prolazi nikakvu drugu tačku u $S$.</p>\n<p>S druge strane, skup {(0, 0), (1, 1), (2, 2), (4, 4)} nije titanijski skup jer linija koja prolazi kroz bilo koje dve tačke u tom skupu takođe prolazi i kroz druge dve tačke.</p>\n<p>Za bilo koji pozitivan ceo broj $N$, neka je $T(N)$ broj kombinacija titaničkog $S$ koje svaka tačka ($x$, $y$) zadovoljava uslov $0 ≤ x$, $y ≤ N$. Dokazano je da $T(1) = 11$, $T(2) = 494$, $T(4) = 33\\,554\\,178$, $T(111)\\bmod {10}^8 = 13\\,500\\,401$ i $T({10}^5)\\bmod {10}^8 = 63\\,259\\,062$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $T({10}^{11})\\bmod {10}^8$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f50c1000cf542c51001e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302084,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-415-titanic-sets"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function titanicSets() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ntitanicSets();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>titanicSets()</code> treba da vrati <code>55859742</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(titanicSets(), 55859742);"}]}}},"pageCont